<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:11:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴西起诉先正达涉嫌环境破坏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-sues-syngenta-alleged-environmental-damage-2024-07-04/</link><description>路透社看到的法庭文件显示，巴西环保机构IBAMA已起诉先正达，指控该化学品公司生产和销售的农药使用浓度远高于法律允许的致癌物，造成“环境损害”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-sues-syngenta-alleged-environmental-damage-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝西方在联合国会议上提出的人权改革的重要呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国周四拒绝了西方主导的人权改革建议，包括要求香港和新疆维吾尔人享有更大自由的呼吁，但接受了盟友的其他建议，试图在联合国会议上捍卫自己的记录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>Bpifrance 计划投资赛诺菲消费者健康业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/bpifrance-eyes-investment-sanofis-consumer-health-business-2024-07-04/</link><description>据彭博社周四报道，Bpifrance 执行董事 Jose Gonzalo 表示，这家公共投资银行正在考虑对赛诺菲消费者健康部门进行潜在投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:37:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/bpifrance-eyes-investment-sanofis-consumer-health-business-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟公布了中国电动汽车关税计算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会周四公布了对中国电动汽车市场为期九个月的调查结果，深入了解了其计算关税的方式以及为支持其最引人注目的贸易案件而收集的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>佩古拉在独立日遭遇不幸，美国人在温布尔登被王淘汰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/independence-day-woe-pegula-american-dumped-out-by-wang-wimbledon-2024-07-04/</link><description>周四，美国独立日温布尔登网球公开赛上，五号种子在第二轮被中国选手王新宇以 6-4 6-7(9) 6-1 淘汰，美国星条旗在温网的杰西卡·佩古拉 (Jessica Pegula) 身上无力飘扬。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/independence-day-woe-pegula-american-dumped-out-by-wang-wimbledon-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>大使称日本与菲律宾防务条约谈判即将结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-philippines-defence-pact-negotiations-nearing-conclusion-ambassador-says-2024-07-04/</link><description>东京驻马尼拉大使周四表示，日本和菲律宾之间关于国防和安全的互惠准入协议的谈判即将结束。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:01:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-philippines-defence-pact-negotiations-nearing-conclusion-ambassador-says-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软削弱印度钻石出口，行业寻求支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构负责人周四表示，由于主要市场中国的需求疲软，印度的切割和成品钻石出口一直步履蹒跚，除非政府向该行业提供支持，否则出口不太可能稳定下来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:36:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>华为高管否认先进芯片短缺将阻碍中国人工智能雄心的观点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为（HWT.UL）的一位高管周四驳斥了最先进人工智能芯片的短缺将阻碍中国成为人工智能领导者的目标的观点，但表示需要创新来解决这个问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>继欧盟电动汽车关税决定后，名爵、蔚来暗示今年汽车价格上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</link><description>在欧盟决定确认对中国进口电动汽车征收关税后，中国品牌名爵和蔚来周四表示，他们可能会在今年晚些时候提高在欧洲的汽车价格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>对欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟将从周五起对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达37.6%的临时关税，这将加剧欧盟迄今为止最大贸易案中与北京的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>独家：在死刑威胁后，企业考虑将台湾员工撤出中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/firms-weigh-removing-taiwan-staff-china-after-death-penalty-threat-2024-07-04/</link><description>四位知情人士表示，在北京表示可能对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑后，一些外国公司正在考虑将台湾员工迁出中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/firms-weigh-removing-taiwan-staff-china-after-death-penalty-threat-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造的电动汽车在迄今为止最大的欧盟贸易案件中被征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-imposes-duties-china-built-evs-leaving-four-months-talks-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟官员表示，欧盟将从周五起对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达 37.6% 的关税，这加剧了布鲁塞尔迄今为止最大贸易案中与北京的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-imposes-duties-china-built-evs-leaving-four-months-talks-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国和欧盟就即将实施的电动汽车关税举行技术会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国商务部在例行新闻发布会上表示，中国和欧洲就中国电动汽车关税问题举行了多轮技术谈判，欧盟委员会将于周四确认这一消息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国利率前景和科技股上涨，亚洲股市吸引了强劲的外资流入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-robust-foreign-inflows-us-rate-outlook-tech-rally-2024-07-04/</link><description>经过两个月的抛售后，外国投资者在 6 月份将大量资金投入亚洲股市，因为美国物价压力的缓解引发了人们对美联储今年降息的希望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-robust-foreign-inflows-us-rate-outlook-tech-rally-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉汽车首次进入中国政府采购清单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</link><description>据中国官方媒体澎湃新闻周四报道，特斯拉最畅销的 Model Y 被列入中国地方政府可以购买作为服务车的电动和插电式混合动力车型清单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>